/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af74f32bb2a0f9600a0f8684492ffafe0e377f2","tid":189293,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我清楚記得當年都係唔識做哩題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你記唔記得標準答案？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜咁多年歷史<br />\n我細個都唔覺有啲咁圖文不符既題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59bc4e9c20daafa60c3c2cafec523f8e2f615f1","tid":189293,"uid":27120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我清楚記得當年都係唔識做哩題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你記唔記得標準答案？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜咁多年歷史<br />\n我細個都唔覺有啲咁圖文不符既題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眨下眼已經year 3 <br />\n仲好記得當時老豆老母又唔識<br />\n又無得開post問<br />\n幾撚無助<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過都係唔記得個答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}